---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Container from '../../components/Container.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';
import Badge from '../../components/Badge.astro';
---

<Base
  title="On the Reasoning Gaps of Large Language Models"
  description="A formal characterization of LLM reasoning failures via computational complexity, with 148,000+ diagnostic evaluations across 11 models."
>
  <Container class="pt-16 pb-24 !max-w-3xl">

    <!-- Pre-print banner -->
    <div class="border border-[var(--color-status-warn-border)] bg-[var(--color-status-warn-muted)] px-4 py-3 mb-10 flex items-center gap-3">
      <Icon name="alert-triangle" size={14} class="text-[var(--color-status-warn)] shrink-0" />
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-status-warn)]">
        Pre-print — not yet published. Under review for NeurIPS 2026.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="label mb-3">Paper</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-mono font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-bright)] leading-[1.1] mb-3">
        On the Reasoning Gaps of Large Language Models: A Formal Characterization
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mt-5">
        <span class="stat-label">Oddur Sigurdsson</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">&middot;</span>
        <span class="stat-label">NeurIPS 2026</span>
        <Badge text="Pre-print" variant="outline" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Download -->
    <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] p-6 mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Download</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-1">Full paper with appendices</p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="/papers/reasoning-gaps.pdf"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider px-5 py-2.5 border-2 border-[var(--color-text-bright)] text-[var(--color-text-bright)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--color-text-bright)] hover:text-[var(--color-bg)] transition-colors hover:no-underline"
        >
          <Icon name="download" size={14} />
          PDF
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] mb-12" />

    <!-- Abstract -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-mono font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] mb-6">Abstract</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Large language models exhibit systematic reasoning failures that resist scaling and prompt engineering. We present a formal framework that characterizes these failures through the lens of computational complexity theory. By mapping the transformer architecture to the complexity class TC&#x2070; (constant-depth threshold circuits), we identify six distinct types of reasoning gaps corresponding to specific complexity-theoretic boundaries: sensitivity gaps (AC&#x2070;), depth gaps (TC&#x2070;/NC&#xB9;), serial composition gaps (bounded-depth vs. linear depth), algorithmic gaps (within P), intractability gaps (NP-hard), and architectural gaps (autoregressive constraints).
        </p>
        <p>
          We construct ReasonGap, a diagnostic benchmark suite of nine procedurally generated tasks (B1&ndash;B9), each targeting a specific gap type with controlled difficulty scaling. Evaluating eleven models from five families &mdash; including GPT-4o, o3, Claude Haiku 4.5, Sonnet 4.6, Llama 3.1, Qwen 2.5, and Mistral &mdash; across 148,068 instances under direct-answer, chain-of-thought, and budget-constrained conditions, we find that chain-of-thought prompting produces a mean accuracy lift of +0.340 for depth and serial composition gaps (Types 2&ndash;3) but only +0.086 for intractability and architectural gaps (Types 5&ndash;6), confirming the framework's central prediction.
        </p>
        <p>
          The framework provides practitioners with a principled basis for determining when prompting strategies can address reasoning limitations versus when tool augmentation or architectural changes are required.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Results -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-mono font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] mb-6">Key Results</h2>

      <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)] p-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="stat-label mb-2">CoT Lift &mdash; Types 2&ndash;3</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400 tabular-nums">+0.340</p>
            <p class="stat-label mt-1">depth &amp; serial gaps</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-16 bg-[var(--color-border)]"></div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="stat-label mb-2">CoT Lift &mdash; Types 5&ndash;6</p>
            <p class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-red-400 tabular-nums">+0.086</p>
            <p class="stat-label mt-1">intractability &amp; architectural gaps</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] p-4">
          <p class="stat-label mb-1">Models</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] tabular-nums">11</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] p-4">
          <p class="stat-label mb-1">Tasks</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] tabular-nums">9</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] p-4">
          <p class="stat-label mb-1">Conditions</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] tabular-nums">3</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)] p-4">
          <p class="stat-label mb-1">Instances</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] tabular-nums">148K</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Taxonomy overview -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-mono font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] mb-6">Gap Taxonomy</h2>
      <div class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-[var(--color-border)] border border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T1</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Sensitivity Gap</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">AC&#x2070; boundary &mdash; CoT helps</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-400 shrink-0">fixable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T2</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Depth Gap</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">TC&#x2070;/NC&#xB9; boundary &mdash; O(log n) CoT</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-400 shrink-0">fixable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T3</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Serial Composition</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">Needs O(n) steps &mdash; O(n) CoT</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-400 shrink-0">fixable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T4</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Algorithmic Gap</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">Complex within P &mdash; tools better</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-amber-400 shrink-0">partial</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T5</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Intractability Gap</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">NP-hard &mdash; fundamentally hard</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-red-400 shrink-0">unfixable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5 shrink-0 w-8">T6</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)]">Architectural Gap</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-0.5">Autoregressive constraint &mdash; structural</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-red-400 shrink-0">unfixable</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Citation -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-mono font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-bright)] mb-6">Citation</h2>
      <pre class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] !bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)]" set:html={`@article{sigurdsson2026reasoning,
  title   = {On the Reasoning Gaps of Large Language Models:
             A Formal Characterization},
  author  = {Sigurdsson, Oddur},
  journal = {Preprint},
  year    = {2026}
}`} />
    </section>

    <!-- Links -->
    <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] mb-8" />
    <div class="flex gap-6">
      <a href="/papers/reasoning-gaps.pdf" class="label hover:text-[var(--color-text-bright)] transition-colors hover:no-underline flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <Icon name="download" size={12} />
        PDF
      </a>
      <a href="/research/reasoning-gaps" class="label hover:text-[var(--color-text-bright)] transition-colors hover:no-underline flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <Icon name="book-open" size={12} />
        Explainer
      </a>
      <a href="/dashboard/project/reasoning-gaps" class="label hover:text-[var(--color-text-bright)] transition-colors hover:no-underline flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <Icon name="bar-chart-3" size={12} />
        Dashboard
      </a>
      <a href="/papers" class="label hover:text-[var(--color-text-bright)] transition-colors hover:no-underline flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <Icon name="arrow-left" size={12} />
        All Papers
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Base>
